# Third-Party Licenses

rasmcore includes the following third-party dependencies. This file lists
direct runtime dependencies and their licenses. For the complete transitive
dependency tree (352 crates), run `cargo metadata` or `cargo-deny`.

## License Summary

All runtime dependencies use permissive licenses (MIT, Apache-2.0, BSD).
When a dependency offers dual licensing (e.g., "MIT OR Apache-2.0"), we
choose the more permissive option (MIT).

**Known issue:** zenjpeg is AGPL-3.0 — tracked for replacement with our
own JPEG encoder (rasmcore-jpeg). See track jpeg-encoder-own_20260328064600Z.

